  <form action="/thingshui/create" method="POST" class="formScript" enctype="multipart/form-data">

    <label for="title">Title:</label>
    <input type="text" name="title" />

    <label for="description">Description:</label>
    <textarea name="description" cols="30" rows="10"></textarea>

    <input type="file" name="imageUrl"/>

    <button type="submit" class="path-text"><img class="icons-btn-path" src="/images/conversations2.png" />"Thing Shui" your Thing</button>

  </form>
</div>

<div>
  <footer class="footerIndex">
    <p>If you want you can write a few words, a memory, a story, journal entry,
      to not forget it or its meaning to you and LET IT GO.</p>
    <br />
    <p>If you need help to stop bringing stuff home, bought or not, 
      try instead to think of whether you really need the object or will a story and picture suffice, and rescue
      its dignity from being another non-essential item in your home.</p>
  </footer>
</div>